  m_text: "<b>Q</b> \u2014 <color=#BFA0FF>Charge tier</color>\r\n<i>Signed closure
    share on the six-step register</i>\r\n<color=#9AA3B2>Charge is given by Q = (\u03C6
    \u2212 2\u03C0)/2\u03C0 relative to full return.</color>\r\n<color=#8FCFC8>Q
    sets the signed charge carried by the certified state. In comparison with experiment,
    this is the baryon charge in units of e.</color>"
