  m_text: "<b>\u20D7S</b> \u2014 <color=#BFA0FF>Contrast step vector</color>\r\n<i>Six-site
    flavour address</i>\r\n<color=#9AA3B2>Gives the discrete step position on the
    six-site register.</color>\r\n<color=#8FCFC8>\u20D7S fixes the flavour content
    of the state. Rest energy is determined separately by the ledger.</color>"
