  m_text: "<b>\u03BB</b> \u2014 <color=#BFA0FF>Radial coherence length</color>\r\n<i>Spatial
    closure scale in femtometres</i>\r\n<color=#9AA3B2>Perfect closure is fixed at
    \u03BB = \u03BB\u2080 with \u03A3\u03B8 = 2\u03C0.</color>\r\n<color=#8FCFC8>Changing
    \u03BB moves the probe away from \u03BB\u2080, sets the radial deviation, and
    updates the ledger output.</color>"
