  m_text: "<b>J</b> \u2014 <color=#BFA0FF>Spin tier</color>\r\n<i>Closure-mode classification</i>\r\n<color=#9AA3B2>Spin-1/2
    fixes the base closure tier. Spin-3/2 fixes the lifted tier within the same certified
    seat family.</color>\r\n<color=#8FCFC8>In empirical comparison, this corresponds
    to the total spin label assigned to the baryon state.</color>"
